description:
Duplicacy backs up your files to many cloud storages with client-side encryption and the highest level of deduplication. This is the full-featured web-based GUI frontend supporting all major operations.

This version can be used without a license if you only need the restore, check, copy, and prune operations.
If you do need to run backups, a fully functional 30-day trial license will be automatically downloaded to enable the backup operation.
After 30 days, a personal or commercial license can be purchased.
